Added schema.org ScholarlyArticle structured data to publications page for enhanced search visibility.

Implemented comprehensive ItemList schema containing individual ScholarlyArticle entries for each publication on the publications page. Each article includes structured metadata for headline, author, publication volume, date published, pagination, URLs, PDF distribution links, descriptions, and impact statements. Added conditional logic to render publications structured data only on the publications page. Enhanced publications page with summary field for improved social media previews. Schema includes proper JSON-LD formatting with position indexing, publication volumes, and data download objects for PDFs. Structured data enables rich snippets in academic search results and improves discoverability of research publications across search engines and academic platforms.
